text:
服务商合作商户收益
1、抖音商户拉新限时补贴100元：例:10 户=1000元，100户=10000元以此类推不但能赚现金流，还能收集自己的新商户资源，方便以后的合作升级。
2、 抖音、快手抽佣5-10%：例:1000元/天*5%=50元/天*30天*100户=150000/月. 商户一直给你合作，这个收益月月都有
3、 视频号团购抽佣10%：例:1000元/天*10%=100元/天*30天*100家=300000/月
trans:
Earnings of the service provider's partners
1. 100-yuan express subsidy for bringing in new merchants on TikTok: For example: 10 merchants = 1,000 yuan, 100 merchants = 10,000 yuan, and so on. You can not only earn cash flow, but also collect your own new merchant resources to facilitate promotion of future cooperation.
2. 5-10% commission for TikTok and Kuaishou: For example: 1,000 yuan/day * 5% = 50 yuan/day * 30 days * 100 merchants = 150,000 yuan/month. If you have been cooperating with the merchants, you will get this income every month.
3. 10% commission for group buying on WeChat Channel: For example: 1,000 yuan/day * 10% = 100 yuan/day * 30 days * 100 merchants= 300,000 yuan/month.
